  "body": "### Version of Hardhat\n\n2.19.1\n\n### What happened?\n\nThere is no hardhat-viem documentation on how to deploy a contract to main or test net. \r\n\n\n### Minimal reproduction steps\n\nI need a walletClient to deploy to a live network right?\r\nthe examples only showq how a contract is deployed using the PublicClient. How can I do it?\r\n\r\n```\r\n    const [testAccount1, testAccount2] = await hre.viem.getWalletClients()\r\n\r\n    const myToken = await testAccount1.deployContract('MyToken')\r\n```\n\n### Search terms\n\n_No response_",
